const [items, setItems] = useState([]);   const [name, setName] = useState("");   const [price, setPrice] = useState("");   const [editingId, setEditingId] = useState(null);   useEffect(() => {     fetch("http://localhost:5000/items")       .then(res => res.json())       .then(data => setItems(data))       .catch(err => console.error(err));   }, []);   const handleAddOrUpdate = () => {     if (!name || !price) return alert("fill");     const itemData = { name, price: Number(price) };     if (editingId !== null) {       fetch(${"http://localhost:5000/items"}/${editingId}, {         method: "PUT",         headers: { "Content-Type": "application/json" },         body: JSON.stringify(itemData)       })         .then(() => {           setEditingId(null);           setName("");           setPrice("");           return fetch("http://localhost:5000/items");         })         .then(res => res.json())         .then(data => setItems(data))         .catch(err => console.error(err));     } else {       fetch("http://localhost:5000/items", {         method: "POST",         headers: { "Content-Type": "application/json" },         body: JSON.stringify(itemData)       })         .then(() => {           setName("");           setPrice("");           return fetch("http://localhost:5000/items");         })         .then(res => res.json())         .then(data => setItems(data))         .catch(err => console.error(err));     }   };   const handleEdit = item => {     setEditingId(item.id);     setName(item.name);     setPrice(item.price);   };   const handleDelete = id => {     if (window.confirm("Are you sure you want to delete this item?")) {       fetch(${"http://localhost:5000/items"}/${id}, { method: "DELETE" })         .then(() => fetch("http://localhost:5000/items"))         .then(res => res.json())         .then(data => setItems(data))         .catch(err => console.error(err));     }   };
